<\/strong>If you are looking for some happening place on New Year&#8217;s Eve around Candolim beach then, head to Sinq. A lounge resort with an outdoor bar, private poolside cabanas and resident DJs playing your favourite list, the club is all set to host you with an amazing party!<br>If you are planning to stay over after the New Year party, you can stay at our property Amor Beach Resort very close to Sinq.<br>Location: SinQ Nightclub Opposite Taj Holiday Village, Aguada Rd, Candolim, Goa<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Curlies, Anjuna<br><\/strong>Planning to welcome the New Year by the beach and enjoy with your friends &amp; loved ones then Curlies is must go-to place.<br>Offering best Goan dishes, mouth-watering desserts, and quirky cocktails, Curlies in Anjuna is located near the Flea Market where you can shop too. So gather your friends and loved ones, head to Curlies for an open beach party.<br>Location: Near Flea Market, Monteiro Vaddo, Anjuna, Goa<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Love Passion Karma, Candolim<br><\/strong>Welcome to one of the amazing and lively night clubs in the vicinity of Candolim beach, Love Passion Karma or famously called as LPK is the perfect venue to welcome your new year.<br>So be a part of the New Year madness at LPK with great food, drinks, music, dance making it thrilling and memorable one for you and your loved ones.<br>Location: Neerul, Candolim, Bardez, Goa.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Caf\u00e9 Lilliput, Anjuna<br><\/strong>One of the oldest beach clubs in Anjuna, Cafe Liliput is the place to enjoy some international food, great DJs and dance.<br>Welcome the new year with bang at this amazing place with your friends and loved ones.<br>Location: Anjuna Beach, Monteiro Vaddo, Anjuna, Goa <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>New Year Boat Party, Panaji<br><\/strong>Be a part of a grand New Year celebration while sailing the River Mandovi. The famous Goan cruises host amazing cruise parties for tourists and locals to welcome the new year in lively ambiance and lovely cruise experience.<br>Location: Mandovi River Jetty, Panaji, Goa<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Titlie, Vagator<br><\/strong>If you want to spend some quiet tme and celebrate with your loved ones in a quiet place, then head to Titlie Culinary bar in Vagator.<br>Get entertained with some live music, performances and DJ spinning some amazing track!<br>Location: Small Vagator, Ozran Beach Rd, Coutinho Vaddo, Anjuna, Goa<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Caf\u00e9 Mambos, Baga<br><\/strong>Enjoy some lively music and live performances from professional artists at Caf\u00e9 Mambos, located in Baga, very close to Tito\u2019s.<br>A not so crowded place, it offers you an open-air lounge with an enclosed dance area for the guests. The pub serves good food and drinks for guests to enjoy a good time.<br>Location: Titos Lane, Baga Calangute, Bardez, Goa<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Purple Martini, Anjuna<br><\/strong>Perched on a cliff offerring a perfect sunset view, Purple Martini in Anjuna is the just the place to start your New Year&#8217;s Eve. This laidback cafe turns into a total party venue at the night begins. Amazing variety of food and a bar to sip some mocktails &amp; cocktails, Purple Martini is another great bet for a New Year\u2019s eve party.<br>Location: St. Anthony praise waddo, near club nyex, Anjuna, Goa<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>When it comes to the best time of the year to party in Goa, it&#8217;s without any doubt, the new year&#8217;s eve. December month always brings out the lights, music and festive eve in the state. With tourists pouring in, there are a lot of events and gigs happening around the state that attracts both [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":535,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[1],"tags":[],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/amorgroupofhotels.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/534"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\